::Prowl/Dark One::

Dark One opens his mouth to yell as he feels a pain in his back. His eyes 
widen as he hears no sound, seeing holes open in his chest as Dinobot's 
cloaked claws go through him. Mechfluid leaks out of his mouth as he goes 
unconscious, sliding down to the floor.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Prowl cringes as he hears Dark One's scream over the silencer. "Couldn't be a 
bit quieter?" he say into the device to Dinobot, moving over to Iron Raptor.

Prowl looks into her eyes, the same excitement he had always felt with her 
entering his systems. She was beautiful, far more beautiful than anything or 
anyone else in the world. He cringes as he thinks of what she could have gone 
through in the hands of the Alliance.

Prowl sighs. This was going to be risky, but he hoped there wern't any voice 
sensors in the room. Prowl deactivates his silencer, walking closer to Iron 
Raptor.

"Its me," he says quietly, placing his hand on her arm, "Are you allright?"
